"Pours a light colored peachy orange color that is cloudy and with a little head.  There is no lacing.  The odor is sour, citrus, orange, lemon, tangerine, sparkling, cognac, slight peach.  The taste is crisp, tart, sour at first but then fresh cut orange, lemon, grapefruit peel, no long aftertaste."
"Sour and refreshing at the same time.  A bit salty but not as much as I was expecting.  The look and smell not all that good but the sour tangy taste is different and enjoyable."
